      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Tilburg University</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Tilburg_University.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Tilburg_University.JPG/330px-Tilburg_University.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Tilburg_University.JPG/500px-Tilburg_University.JPG 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Tilburg_University.JPG/960px-Tilburg_University.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Tilburg_University.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tilburg University <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Tilburg University</b>,<br />\na public <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Research_university\">research university</a> specializing in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_science\">social and behavioral sciences</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economics\">economics</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Law\">law</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business\">business</a> sciences, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theology\">theology</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Humanities\">humanities</a>, located in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tilburg\">Tilburg</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_Brabant\">North Brabant</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Netherlands\">The Netherlands</a>.\nThe university was founded in 1927 as the <i>Roman Catholic University of Commerce</i>, in 1938, 1963 and 1986 renamed to <i>Catholic Economic University</i>, <i>Catholic University Tilburg</i> and <i>Catholic University Brabant</i> respectively, to finally carry the current name in 2002.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Events_2011\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events 2011</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tilburg_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Mohamed_Abbadi\" title=\"Mohamed Abbadi\">Mohamed Abbadi</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Sander_Bakkes&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Sander Bakkes (page does not exist)\">Sander Bakkes</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Max_Euwe\" title=\"Max Euwe\">Max Euwe</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Johanna_Hellemons\" title=\"Johanna Hellemons\">Johanna Hellemons</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Henk_Koppelaar\" title=\"Henk Koppelaar\">Henk Koppelaar</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aske_Plaat\" title=\"Aske Plaat\">Aske Plaat</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Eric_Postma\" title=\"Eric Postma\">Eric Postma</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fritz_Reul\" title=\"Fritz Reul\">Fritz Reul</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pieter_Spronck\" title=\"Pieter Spronck\">Pieter Spronck</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events_2011\">Events 2011</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tilburg_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Events 2011\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:TheRedBrick2.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d3/TheRedBrick2.JPG/300px-TheRedBrick2.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"224\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/d/d3/TheRedBrick2.JPG 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TheRedBrick2.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Red Brick, where the <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a> events took place <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/16th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"16th Computer Olympiad\">16th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_13\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 13\">Advances in Computer Games 13</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WCCC_2011\" title=\"WCCC 2011\">WCCC 2011</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WCSC_2011\" title=\"WCSC 2011\">WCSC 2011</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tilburg_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#FromMaastrichttoTilburg\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">From Maastricht to Tilburg</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#31_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 31, No. 2</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#FromTilburgtoLeiden\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">From Tilburg to Leiden</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 4</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tilburg_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tilburg_University\">Tilburg University from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tilburguniversity.edu/\">Tilburg University homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tilburguniversity.edu/research/institutes-and-research-groups/ticc/csai/\">Tilburg Centre for Creative Computing (TiCC)</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tilburg_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo by Ron Maijen, May 22, 2011, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.inyourpocket.com/Netherlands/Tilburg\">Tilburg city guide by In Your Pocket</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> (<b>2008</b>) <i>From Maastricht to Tilburg</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ticc.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content31-2.htm\">ICGA Journal Vol. 31, No. 2 - June 2008</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo by <a href=\"/Gerd_Isenberg\" title=\"Gerd Isenberg\">Gerd Isenberg</a> during <a href=\"/WCCC_2011\" title=\"WCCC 2011\">WCCC 2011</a>, <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a> just leaves the builing</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301014050\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.629 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\n